About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Meet Kapil Sharma | Episode 90
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

#kapilsharma #sandeepmaheshwari

snippet.title: Exploring Amritsar With Kapil Sharma | Tere Gully Mein EP 36 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
On this episode of Tera Gully Mein, we met Kapil Sharma and had a trip down memory lane in Amritsar. From binging on buttery Amritsari Kulchas  at  Kartar's Pehalwan Kulcha to devouring some divine Amritsari Kulfa ar  A - One Kulfa, Kamiya and Kapil experienced a food coma at Amritsar. 

Kapil also showed us around his Amritsar home and the theatre Punjab Naatshala where he previously worked at. He spoke to us about his childhood, his struggling journey, his battle with depression, his marriage life, the upcoming film Zwigato and much more. 

Kamiya Jani & Kapil Sharma had a phenomenal time exploring Amritsar. Hope you enjoy the video too!

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. snippet.title: NEW! Baalveer S3 - Ep 1 - 18 Mar  2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 1: Baalveer Ki Entry
-------------------------------------------------
The hero of Dharti Lok, Baalveer, prepares to welcome his mother by decorating the area with air lamps. Baalveer wants things to be ideal because his mum will be visiting in two months. He pays a covert visit to Dharti Lok to get her a particular gift. He searches frantically for something to give, but nothing appeals to him. Baalveer runs into this girl while looking for the ideal present for his mother. Which girl is she? Discover Baalveer's new world-saving quests by watching the episode!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3722 - 18 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3722: Bhide Hai Pareshaan
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone has been speculating about the idea of Tapu Sena as they have invited all the members of the society to the clubhouse. Bhide is worried and wants to know about the idea, he plans to learn the art of hypnosis to get Tapu Sena under his control. He stops Sonu from going to the clubhouse for the preparations and asks her about their surprise plan. He also tries to eavesdrop on Tapu Sena's conversation at the clubhouse, he is caught by Tapu Sena and is asked to wait till the evening. Watch the episode.  

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3722, 18 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000214024

snippet.title: Sunday Brunch With Kareena Kapoor Khan Presented By Cordelia Cruises EP 98 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Our Editor-in-Chief, Kamiya Jani, enjoys traveling and is always rating destinations, much like our guest on this show, who ranks boys in the film Kabhi Khushi Kabhi Gum!

On this episode of Sunday Brunch presented by Cordelia Cruise, we met the Bollywood diva Kareena Kapoor Khan.

She spoke to us about her love for Chinese cuisine, Kapoor family‚Äôs lavish brunches, her journey to Bollywood, her show What Women Want with Mirchi Plus, and a lot more. 

We also played a fun quiz with her 'Life Onboard presented by Cordelia Cruises' where she revealed her travel stories & her future travel plans with her girl gang & family.

snippet.title: NEW! Baalveer S3 - Ep 2 - 19 Mar  2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 2: Baalveer Kasam Kaal
-------------------------------------------------
When Himbaash Lok's evil fairy, Aageel attacks his mother, Baalveer saves her. It was later revealed that Udaaka Lok's chief Maha Mahi Mutaan was testing Baalveer's abilities. Everyone admires Baalveer's strength and how he dealt with Aageel. Meanwhile, Himbaash Lok's fairy, Aageel brags about her extraordinary magical abilities, known as "Maha Jadu," with which she is now capable of defeating the ultimate hero, Baalveer. Maha Mahi Mutaan of Udaaka Lok warns Baalveer about his impending arrival and advises him to cut ties with his mother. Why was Baalveer given such dire warnings? How will Baalveer defeat Udaaka Lok's new nemesis? Keep an eye out!

Nikah Episode 59 - [Eng Sub] - Haroon Shahid - Zainab Shabbir - 19th March 2023  - HAR PAL GEO

Nikah is a powerful and inspiring story of a young girl‚Äôs fight for her social and religious rights. 
Opinionated and confident by nature, Anusha is a beautiful young girl who knows how to stand up for her rights. After losing her mother at a young age, Anusha has been brought up by her aunt, Umaima with a lot of love and care. Umamia is a bit hesitant about Anusha‚Äôs assertiveness and often makes her understand. 
Class fellows and best friends, Anusha and Haris are in love with each other and soon plan to marry. On the contrary, Hamdaan is a handsome young man who belongs to a wealthy family and is the only son of his father. He falls in love with Anusha on his very first meeting with her however is respectful of Anusha‚Äôs choices.
Anusha‚Äôs hope and dreams come crashing down when Haris challenges her thoughts. The supposedly liberal fabric of Haris and his family is exposed when Anusha takes a stand for her rights. After losing everything, will Anusha stay true to herself and fight against all odds? Despite everything, will Anusha realize her true admirer and supporter in form of Hamdaan?

Writer: Nuzhat Saman
Director: Zahid Mehmood

Tere Bin Episode 24 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 16th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Hello friends, today, on 18 march 2023 Saturday, I am presenting to you all the  Papmochani Ekadashi vrat katha of Chaitra Krishna Paksha Ekadashi . Papmochani Ekadashi  means Ekadashi which destroys sins. Keeping fast on the day of Papmochani Ekadashi results in salvation along with the elimination of all sins. Papmochani Ekadashi comes before Chaitra Navratri. On this day, Chaturbhuji form of Lord Vishnu is worshiped by law and we must listen Ekadashi vrat katha. 

According to Papmochani Ekadashi ki katha kahani, Yudhishthira asked - Lord Krishna! Now please explain the great significance of Ekadashi of Chaitra Krishna Paksha. Hey Madhusudan! What is the name of this Ekadashi? Which god is worshiped in this and what is the law of this fast? Lord Shri Krishna said - Rajendra! Ekadashi of Krishna Paksha of Chaitra month is called Papamochini Ekadashi. Many sins of humans are destroyed due to the effect of his fast. I will tell you the story of this fastthe meritorious sages and Apsara Manjugosha lost track of time and indulged in love for 57 years. When sage regained consciousness, he repented of the sin he had committed. After  Papmochani Ekadashi vrat, the meritorious sage got rid of sin and he again got into austerities. Apsara Manjughosha got rid of vampire vagina by fasting Papmochani Ekadashi and she went to the heavenly world wearing a divine body. The best man who observes Papmochani Ekadashi and listens Ekadashi ki kahani all his sins are destroyed. By reading and listening #Ekadashivratkatha, one gets the fruit of the donation 1000 cows.  Papmochani ekadashi fast is very pious.
In video of Papmochini ekadashi katha, Lord krishna is telling significance and importance of papmochani ekadashi vrat. people who perform papmochani ekadashi vrat, they get rid from all of their sins no matter how big their sins were. Lord Vishnu bless that person and take him to vaikuntha dham in the end.
Papmochani Ekadashi Saturday, March 18, 2023

Hello friends, today, on 18 march 2023 Saturday, I am presenting to you all the  Papmochani Ekadashi vrat katha of Chaitra Krishna Paksha Ekadashi . Papmochani Ekadashi  means Ekadashi which destroys sins. Keeping fast on the day of Papmochani Ekadashi results in salvation along with the elimination of all sins. Papmochani Ekadashi comes before Chaitra Navratri. On this day, Chaturbhuji form of Lord Vishnu is worshiped by law and we must listen Ekadashi vrat katha. 

According to Papmochani Ekadashi ki katha kahani, Yudhishthira asked - Lord Krishna! Now please explain the great significance of Ekadashi of Chaitra Krishna Paksha. Hey Madhusudan! What is the name of this Ekadashi? Which god is worshiped in this and what is the law of this fast? Lord Shri Krishna said - Rajendra! Ekadashi of Krishna Paksha of Chaitra month is called Papamochini Ekadashi. Many sins of humans are destroyed due to the effect of his fast. I will tell you the story of this fastthe meritorious sages and Apsara Manjugosha lost track of time and indulged in love for 57 years. When sage regained consciousness, he repented of the sin he had committed. After  Papmochani Ekadashi vrat, the meritorious sage got rid of sin and he again got into austerities. Apsara Manjughosha got rid of vampire vagina by fasting Papmochani Ekadashi and she went to the heavenly world wearing a divine body. The best man who observes Papmochani Ekadashi and listens Ekadashi ki kahani all his sins are destroyed. By reading and listening #Ekadashivratkatha, one gets the fruit of the donation 1000 cows.  Papmochani ekadashi fast is very pious.
In video of Papmochini ekadashi katha, Lord krishna is telling significance and importance of papmochani ekadashi vrat. people who perform papmochani ekadashi vrat, they get rid from all of their sins no matter how big their sins were. Lord Vishnu bless that person and take him to vaikuntha dham in the end.
Papmochani Ekadashi Saturday, March 18, 2023

snippet.title: Oscars: RRR's Naatu Naatu Honored With EPIC Performance
snippet.description: Rahul Sipligunj and Kaala Bhairava sing their 'RRR' song, 'Naatu Naatu,' in an epic dance number at the 95th Academy Awards. The movie later makes history as it becomes the first Indian feature film to win an Oscar, with the track's composer and lyricist, M.M. Keeravaani and Chandrabose, nabbing Best Original Song. The 2023 Oscars aired on ABC.
